import React from "react"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom"

import HomePage from "./pages/HomePage"

export default function App() {
  return (
    <>
        <Router>

            <Routes>
                <Route path='/' index={true} children={<HomePage />} />
            </Routes>
        </Router>
    </>
  )
}
